---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Cover from '../components/Cover.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About · DwellWell Property Care"
  description="DwellWell is the managed operator of record for property maintenance and preservation. One point of contact, vetted contractors, every job documented from intake to closeout."
  active="about"
>
  <Cover
    eyebrow="About DwellWell"
    title="The managed operator of record."
    sub="DwellWell coordinates property maintenance and preservation from intake to closeout. One point of contact, vetted contractors, every job documented."
    titleWidth="16ch"
    subWidth="60ch"
  />

  <main>
    <!-- WHO WE ARE -->
    <section class="container section">
      <div class="split">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="section-head__rule section-head__rule--tall"></span>
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;"><span class="eyebrow__label">Who we are</span></div>
            <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:16ch;">A single operator for property work</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="body" style="margin-bottom:20px;">DwellWell is the managed operator of record for property maintenance and preservation. We take responsibility for the work itself, coordinating vetted contractors, managing each job, and documenting it through to closeout.</p>
          <p class="muted body-size" style="margin-bottom:28px;">We serve property managers, owners, and asset holders who want maintenance and preservation handled by one accountable party, across residential properties and vacant assets alike.</p>
          <div class="callout-neutral">
            <p style="margin:0;">You hold one relationship. We coordinate everything behind it, from the first work order to the closeout record.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container"><div class="divider"></div></div>

    <!-- OUR MODEL -->
    <section class="container section">
      <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:14px;">
        <span class="section-head__rule"></span>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;"><span class="eyebrow__label">Our model</span></div>
          <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:20ch;">How the operator model works</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="lead-indent">Clients submit work orders. DwellWell coordinates the rest and stays the single point of contact throughout.</p>

      <div class="model-grid">
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="model-num"><span>1</span></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px;">You submit a work order</h3>
            <p class="muted">Clients send requests through a single channel, for one property or many.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card model-card--dark">
          <div class="model-num model-num--light"><span>2</span></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--cool-white);">DwellWell coordinates</h3>
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--steel-grey);margin:0;">We handle dispatch, management, documentation, and closeout with vetted contractors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="model-num"><span>3</span></div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:8px;">You deal with DwellWell</h3>
            <p class="muted">One point of contact from intake through closeout. You never chase a contractor.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container"><div class="divider"></div></div>

    <!-- ACCOUNTABILITY -->
    <section class="container section">
      <div class="split">
        <div>
          <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
            <span class="section-head__rule section-head__rule--tall"></span>
            <div>
              <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:12px;"><span class="eyebrow__label">Accountability</span></div>
              <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:16ch;">Accountability sits with DwellWell</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="muted body-size" style="max-width:60ch;padding-left:32px;">The work is ours to manage and ours to stand behind. Nothing is simply handed off to a contractor and left there.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="acct-list">
          <div class="acct-row">
            <div class="acct-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="#4A8BB5" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7 3h7l4 4v14H6V4"></path><path d="M14 3v4h4"></path><path d="M9.5 12h5"></path><path d="M9.5 15.5h5"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:6px;">Every job documented</h3>
              <p class="muted">Photos, notes, and a closeout record on every work order.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="acct-row">
            <div class="acct-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="#4A8BB5" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3 4 6v5c0 4.5 3.2 7.8 8 9.5 4.8-1.7 8-5 8-9.5V6z"></path><path d="M9 11.5 11 13.5 15.5 9"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:6px;">Owned, not referred out</h3>
              <p class="muted">Accountability sits with DwellWell, not the contractor.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="acct-row">
            <div class="acct-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="#4A8BB5" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12a7 7 0 0 1 14 0"></path><rect x="3.5" y="12" width="3.5" height="6" rx="1.5"></rect><rect x="17" y="12" width="3.5" height="6" rx="1.5"></rect><path d="M19 18v.5a3 3 0 0 1-3 3h-3"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size:20px;margin-bottom:6px;">One record, one invoice</h3>
              <p class="muted">You receive a complete closeout record and a single invoice per job.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- FOOT CTAs (Cool White band, Steel Blue emphasis divider) -->
  <section class="foot-cta">
    <div class="container" style="padding-block:clamp(56px,9vw,88px);">
      <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:36px;max-width:22ch;">Two ways to work with DwellWell</h2>
      <div class="cards-2">
        <div class="path-card">
          <span class="path-card__kicker">For clients</span>
          <h3 class="h3">Hand maintenance to one accountable operator.</h3>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Tell us what you need handled and we coordinate it from intake to closeout.</p>
          <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/contact">Start a conversation</a>
        </div>
        <div class="path-card">
          <span class="path-card__kicker">For contractors</span>
          <h3 class="h3">Join our network of vetted contractors.</h3>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Receive coordinated, documented work orders with a single point of contact.</p>
          <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="/join-as-contractor">Join as a contractor</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .section { padding: clamp(56px, 9vw, 96px) var(--gutter); }
  .divider { height: 0.5px; background: var(--steel-grey); }
  .body { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--midnight); margin: 0; max-width: 64ch; }
  .body-size { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; max-width: 64ch; }
  .muted { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--cool-slate); margin: 0; }
  .lead-indent { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--cool-slate); margin: 0 0 44px; max-width: 62ch; padding-left: 32px; }
  .cards-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }

  .split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: clamp(32px, 6vw, 72px); align-items: start; }
  .section-head__rule--tall { min-height: 64px; }

  .callout-neutral { border: 0.5px solid var(--steel-grey); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px 22px; max-width: 64ch; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--midnight); }

  /* Our model */
  .model-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(264px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
  .model-card { padding: 30px; background: var(--cool-white); border: 1px solid var(--steel-grey); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
  .model-card--dark { background: var(--midnight); border-color: var(--midnight); }
  .model-num { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--midnight); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex: 0 0 auto; }
  .model-num span { font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; color: var(--cool-white); }
  .model-num--light { background: var(--cool-white); }
  .model-num--light span { color: var(--midnight); }

  /* Accountability */
  .acct-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .acct-row { display: flex; gap: 18px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 24px; background: var(--cool-white); border: 1px solid var(--steel-grey); border-radius: 8px; }
  .acct-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--midnight); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex: 0 0 auto; }

  /* Foot CTAs */
  .foot-cta { background: var(--cool-white); border-top: 1px solid var(--steel-blue); }
  .path-card { padding: 32px; background: var(--cool-white); border: 1px solid var(--steel-grey); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .path-card__kicker { font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cool-slate); }
</style>
